You aren't from this kingdom, but you've heard a lot about it.
The king has called for adventurers, so here you are.
You are now tasked with the most difficult quest known to man, find the king's long lost son.
The quest isn't dangerous, but all before you have failed.
Explore the vast lands, meet interesting townsfolk, and learn about the kingdom's ancient language.
Oh, and welcome to Advantara.
